{"questionId": "68b576c1-9de8-41d3-9840-538d4edcd113_15", "correctAnswer": "15", "section": "Math", "steps": [{"title": "Set the function $C(t) = 247$", "content": "$$240\\left(\\tfrac{53}{52}\\right)^{t-15} + 7 = 247$$<br/>Subtract 7:<br/>$$240\\left(\\tfrac{53}{52}\\right)^{t-15} = 240$$<br/>Divide by 240:<br/>$$\\left(\\tfrac{53}{52}\\right)^{t-15} = 1$$"}, {"title": "Solve the exponent", "content": "Any nonzero base raised to the $0$ power equals $1$, so $t - 15 = 0$, giving $t = 15$.<br/><br/>The answer is <strong>15</strong>."}]}